      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamiami%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "Locals say Tamiami is pronounced “tam‑my‑am‑my,” not “tam‑my‑am‑my” with a hard “my” sound.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        4
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamiami%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Tamiami sits just 14 miles west of downtown Miami, making it a quick escape from the city’s bustle.",
