      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamiami%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The town’s geographic coordinates are 25.7587° N latitude and 80.3984° W longitude, placing it firmly in Miami‑Dade County.",
